data.description: Welcome to this 2017 custom built Home in SW Cape Coral! At almost 2000 sq. ft. this home features 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths with a den and ***all assessments have been PAID! The home is being OFFERED FURNISHED with TOMMY BAHAMA FURNITURE & window coverings by HUNTER DOUGLAS! On arrival, you will notice the upgraded pavered driveway, real brick facade & screened entry way to keep the bugs at bay. Beautiful light fixtures & luxury ceiling fans throughout. Gorgeous luxury vinyl plank flooring & crown molding throughout main living areas. The open kitchen features a large pantry, pendant lights, SS appliances, luxury granite countertops with a modern tile backsplash that brings it all together. Huge master bath shower features multiple shower heads & dual granite sinks. Bedrooms are good size & offer plenty of natural sunlight. Saltwater pool has a large sitting area under cover for summer storms. This home is equipped with 4 electrical lanai shutters & manual accordion shutters for storm protection, easy to close & go! Pool area has a 2"concrete pad under the pavers, no weeds, or sagging pavers:)Lots of deck space for entertaining! Great location, close to schools, shopping & beaches!
